data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Guyton with no HOA. This home sits on 1/2 acre with a big backyard and new storage shed equipped with electricity. Primary bedroom has a primary bathroom with double vanities. Laundry closet is in the hallway, 1 car garage off the kitchen.
